<h1 style="margin: 0px 0px 0px 12px; ">Applicants with Disabilities</h1><br />
    <table summary="" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="578">
        <tr valign="top">
            <td style="padding: 6px 12px 0px 12px; height: 100%" valign="top">
    Bank of America complies with the Americans with Disabilities Act (ADA) and similar state laws prohibiting disability discrimination. We are committed to ensuring that our online application process provides an equal employment opportunity to all U.S. job seekers, including individuals with disabilities. 
    <br><br>
    If you are interested in an opportunity with Bank of America, please <a href="http://careers.bankofamerica.com/jobsearch.aspx">search for available opportunities</a> and complete and submit an online application.  If you have a disability and you believe you need a reasonable accommodation in order to search for a job opening or to submit an online application, please contact us by calling <b>1.877.760.2076</b>.  This is a dedicated line designed exclusively to assist disabled job seekers whose disability prevents them from being able to apply online.  Only messages left for this purpose will be returned.  A response to your request may take up to two business days.
    </td>
    </tr>
    <tr><td>&nbsp;</td></tr>
    <tr valign="top">
            <td style="padding: 6px 12px 0px 12px; height: 100%" valign="top">
            <b>Please note:</b>
            <ul>  
                <li>If you have already been contacted by a recruiter for a specific job posting and require reasonable accommodation to further participate in the applicant process, you may discuss your need for reasonable accommodation directly with the recruiter.</li>  
                <li>Messages left at the 1.877.760.2076 number that are for other purposes, such as following up on an application or technical issues not related to a disability, will not receive a response. </li>
            </ul>
            </td>
    </tr>
    <tr><td>&nbsp;</td></tr>
    <tr valign="top">
            <td style="padding: 6px 12px 0px 12px; height: 100%" valign="top">
